text: Adama Coulibaly (born 25 January 1998) is a Malian basketball player for Saint-Louis Basket and the Malian national team.Afrobasket.com profile She represented Mali at the 2019 Women's Afrobasket.2019 Women's Afrobasket profile ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Expatriate basketball people in Belgium Category:Power forwards (basketball) Category:Malian expatriate sportspeople in Belgium Category:Malian women's basketball players Category:Sportspeople from Bamako
